snippet.title: Eternal Strands - Cast & Combine Trailer | Xbox Partner Preview October 2024
snippet.description:
Cast and combine frost, flame, and kinetic magic to take down massive 25-meter foes in the new fantasy action-adventure game, Eternal Strands. Coming early 2025.

Coming Day One to Game Pass!
